{"tid":1763491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民狂投訴TVB新聞偏頗  「花哥」袁志偉內部信：廣播局話所有指控唔成立","createTime":"2019-11-30T11:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T15:27:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9cc39c2b64fb19b2cd4a6adfd94094a77e4276","tid":1763491,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"近日有調查話，電視廣播（511，TVB）嘅公信力急速下挫，同中共喉舌近乎睇齊，無他，喺過去接近半年反修例示威中，無線新聞嘅角度好多時候都有偏幫政權之嫌，網民向廣播局嘅投訴數以千計。<br />\n<br />\n無線新聞部高層「花哥」袁志偉唔知係咪覺得有壓力，近日發信同內部嘅人講一單好消息：「好多人投訴TVB新聞唔公正，唔客觀，唔準確，批評偏黃同偏藍嘅意見都有。不過，廣播局今日已經回覆咗話經過長時間及非常審慎嘅調查同研究，所有投訴都唔成立！」<br />\n<br />\n個調查結果嘅覆函，花哥冇公開，只係叫同事搵採訪主任拎嚟睇。呢封自high嘅內部信，其實都冇辦法扭轉大眾對於呢間俗稱CCTVB嘅電視台印象。事實上，作為新聞部員工，外部承受住龐大輿論壓力，內部連着「黑衫」出鏡都畀高層鬧，士氣低落真係少不免，最好嘅改善方法，就係檢討下自己係咪永遠都只係幫警察同藍絲說話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575099514_1d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575099514_1d46.jpg&h=73700d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「花哥」袁志偉（左）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191130/60327661\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60327661&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipfylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=791eebd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60327661&h=21734672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191130/60327661</a>"},{"pid":"fb53d032bb25b63bcd59146a8c93ef4ff6d1c8c6","tid":1763491,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6fc0b8ce14b4b20786ba57c2d64a8a999e797a","tid":1763491,"uid":121580,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-